Package: comptoxtools
Title: Tools for the EPA CompTox Chemical Dashboard API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to search and retrieve chemical data from the
    EPA CompTox Chemical Dashboard API, including chemical identity information
    (DTXSID, CAS-RN, SMILES, preferred name), structural and physico-chemical
    property data, and structure images. Also includes tools for ToxPrint
    chemotype analysis (proportion calculations, per-chemical counts, and
    enrichment analyses), UMAP dimensionality reduction and visualisation, and
    a utility to recover CAS registry numbers that Excel has incorrectly
    reformatted as dates.
